title: Ep. - 355 - LALA KENT FROM VANDERPUMP RULES BRIAN MOYLAN TALKS REAL HOUSEWIVES
description:
Lala Kent from Bravo’s Vanderpump Rules talks about becoming a mother, her daughter Ocean’s birth story, stories from her new book, and filming next season of the show.

 

Brian Moylan, author of ‘The Real Story Behind the Real Housewives’ reviews the premiere season of Real Housewives of New York and behind the scenes of the shows.
